				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">the designers would put in a toggle to let you confirm trades before you GIVE AWAY ITEMS YOU <span style="text-decoration: underline">WANTED</span> TO YOUR STOOPID PET.
<br />

<br />
Last night, after a nice playing session in Nurga, I had four named mob drops.  I was going to hand them to my shaman, so I could log in my druid and pick them up for transport to my bazaar mule.  I hand the shaman the 4 items and hit trade.  But the items are lore, and my shaman already had one of them.  Trade cancelled.
<br />

<br />
So, I do the trade again, this time excluding the duplicated item.  I hit trade, glance over at my shaman screen, and get a sick feeling in my stomach.  
<br />

<br />
I'd just handed the 3 remaining items to Jabober.  
<br />

<br />
Whisp</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
